they'd lose the rights

12:32.530 --> 12:35.741
if they didn't make the film
in the next six days.

12:35.782 --> 12:40.413
After a two-hour search,
they found their entire cast.

12:40.454 --> 12:43.541
They also proved useful six
days later at the wrap party.

12:43.581 --> 12:46.584
I almost never get recognized
as the Invisible Girl.

12:46.626 --> 12:48.254
I can't believe you saw me.

12:48.295 --> 12:51.048
Well, I-I thought it was
