13:02.560 --> 13:04.562
Did his fishing line break, too?

13:04.602 --> 13:07.022
DeBRIE:
Well, my acting career is over.

13:07.064 --> 13:10.317
Oh, don't say that. You've got
to say, "Keep the dream alive."

13:10.359 --> 13:11.735
That's what helps me.

13:11.777 --> 13:13.611
Well, this is what's helping me.

13:13.653 --> 13:15.739
- Oh.
- It's really good.

13:15.781 --> 13:17.783
