grape juice.

13:17.824 --> 13:20.244
But then he'd add five dollars
to our credit card.

13:20.286 --> 13:22.620
Well, here is to
our acting addiction.

13:22.662 --> 13:23.621
Yep.

13:23.663 --> 13:25.665
May we never be cured.

13:25.707 --> 13:27.960
Are you crying? Oh, I'm crying.

13:28.001 --> 13:30.670
Oh, it's a nosebleed.

13:30.712 --> 13:32.214
(DeBrie gasping)

13:32.256 --> 13:34.467
Oh, thank you so much.

13:34.508 --> 13:36.594
