13:36.634 --> 13:38.137
- You're neat!
- You're neat.

13:38.178 --> 13:39.555
(laughing):
You're neat.

13:39.597 --> 13:41.056
You're neat.

13:43.850 --> 13:45.727
NARRATOR: And after a
not-very-cute meet-cute,

13:45.769 --> 13:48.272
