DeBrie's behavior delightful,

13:48.314 --> 13:50.274
even when the methadone
made her think

13:50.316 --> 13:53.277
she was a piece of toast.

13:53.319 --> 13:55.279
There, now I can see

13:55.321 --> 13:58.240
a pretty face under all that
butter substitute.

13:58.282 --> 14:00.326
And I recognize you
from somewhere,

14:00.367 --> 14:04.037
but it's not the Fantastic Four;
it's from somewhere else.

14:04.079 --> 14:06.499
I've done some things
I'm not proud of.

14:06.540 --> 14:08.083
Episodics? Been there.

14:08.125 --> 14:11.044
It wasn't episodic.

14:11.086 --> 14:12.588
She had been in a series

14:12.630 --> 14:14.047
of soft-core porn movies
about women

14:14.089 --> 14:15.882
leading straight men
into gay sex,

14:15.924 --> 14:18.135
- called Straight Bait.
- This is my brother. He's gay.

14:18.177 --> 14:19.719
If you want to have sex with me,

14:19.761 --> 14:21.763
