with him first.

14:21.805 --> 14:25.142
And if you don't want to have
sex with her, you must be gay.

14:25.184 --> 14:27.353
I'll show you how not gay I am.

14:30.272 --> 14:32.316
She did six of these movies,

14:32.358 --> 14:35.277
and after lunch,
did three more.

14:35.319 --> 14:37.029
It's nice to be
recognized though.

14:37.070 --> 14:38.822
Marky Bark--
sometimes he doesn't know

14:38.864 --> 14:40.907
when I'm in the same room.

14:40.949 --> 14:42.284
And sometimes it feels like

14:42.326 --> 14:43.846
it's not the face blindness,
you know?

14:43.869 --> 14:45.829
It's the same
with me and Lindsay.

14:45.871 --> 14:48.207
I know she's trying,
but she doesn't believe

14:48.248 --> 14:50.209
in my acting career.

14:50.250 --> 14:52.961
Maybe she's right. I've yet
to make more money as an actor

14:53.003 --> 14:55.005
than I ever did as a doctor.

14:55.047 --> 14:56.840
And that's with
Country-Wide behind me.

14:56.882 --> 14:59.051
You're... wait, you're a doctor?
You can write scripts?

14:59.092 --> 15:01.011
Well, I like to think so.

15:01.053 --> 15:04.390
You should never give up a dream
if you can write scripts.

15:04.431 --> 15:07.393
You seem like you'd be
a good doctor/actor.

15:07.434 --> 15:09.728
It was the first
positive reinforcement

15:09.769 --> 15:11.855
Tobias had had since India.

15:11.897 --> 15:15.484
You remind me of
Billy Crystal... Mmm, mmm!

15:15.526 --> 15:18.195
It would have broken
Tobias's heart if he knew

15:18.237 --> 15:20.364
she was about to say
"Billy Crystal Meth,"

15:20.406 --> 15:21.823
a funny drug dealer.

15:21.865 --> 15:25.369
Uh, I... got a bit carried away

15:25.411 --> 15:27.663
when you compared me
to Billy Crystal.

15:27.705 --> 15:30.207
You remind me
of Billy Crystal...

15:30.249 --> 15:33.793
Once again, she was going
to say "Billy Crystal Meth."

15:33.835 --> 15:36.547
I'm sorry, but, DeBrie,
