15:49.518 --> 15:52.062
Whoa. Whoa.
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

15:52.104 --> 15:55.815
Did you see my Straight Bait
movie of the same name?

15:55.857 --> 15:58.193
(singsong):
Coincidence.

15:58.235 --> 15:59.737
We should be together.

15:59.778 --> 16:01.154
We should run away.

16:01.196 --> 16:02.573
(stammering)

16:02.615 --> 16:03.865
Oh, my gosh.

16:03.907 --> 16:05.534
Well, this is happening so fast.

16:05.576 --> 16:07.119
Well, what do I do
about Lindsay?

16:07.160 --> 16:09.913
I mean, can I just improv my way
