16:21.425 --> 16:23.761
that he was leaving Lindsay
in a phone call.

16:23.802 --> 16:25.262
...for I have met someone.

16:25.304 --> 16:26.888
It's not important who it is.

16:26.930 --> 16:28.474
(laughs):
It's Sue Storm.

16:28.515 --> 16:30.643
I'm so sorry,
but DeBrie believes in me,

16:30.684 --> 16:32.603
