16:32.645 --> 16:35.689
If you're wondering what "too"
referred to, it was this:

16:35.731 --> 16:37.023
Let's do this.

16:37.065 --> 16:38.525
Blackout.

16:38.567 --> 16:40.736
And scene, as they say.

16:40.778 --> 16:42.139
Her heart stopped!
She-She's dying!

16:42.154 --> 16:44.615
Please, someone!
She had too much butter!

16:44.657 --> 16:46.116
- She's a very famous actress!
- Someone say "butter" out here?

16:46.158 --> 16:47.867
Oh, my God,
that's a butter face.

16:47.909 --> 16:50.162
- How much butter did the patient have?
- I don't know.

16:50.203 --> 16:51.997
- A Star Trek chess set's worth.
- Damn it, that Swappigans

16:52.038 --> 16:54.458
puts more people in
this hospital. Make way, people!

16:54.500 --> 16:55.709
We got a 61-year-old male

16:55.751 --> 16:57.169
