coming through.

16:57.210 --> 16:58.420
You have to wait outside, sir.

16:58.462 --> 16:59.713
Be careful of her face!

16:59.755 --> 17:01.507
She's an actress!

17:01.548 --> 17:03.258
(loud sobbing)

17:03.300 --> 17:04.843
It's worth noting that Tobias

17:04.884 --> 17:07.179
had heard this hospital
in Orange County

17:07.220 --> 17:09.765
