grew dire enough

22:38.802 --> 22:40.053
for this to happen.

22:40.095 --> 22:41.972
We're broke.

22:42.014 --> 22:43.932
But you can't sell
your Fantastic Four costume.

22:43.974 --> 22:45.308
I mean, that would be
like a fisherman

22:45.350 --> 22:47.352
selling his fishing costume.

22:47.393 --> 22:49.604
No, I was gonna
have sex with him.

22:49.646 --> 22:51.188
For money.

22:51.230 --> 22:52.899
What? No. Put that back on.

22:52.941 --> 22:54.901
You don't have to
degrade yourself this way.

22:54.943 --> 22:57.070
Hey, I'm not a thing.

22:57.112 --> 22:59.322
Hey, I am a Thing.

22:59.364 --> 23:01.908
And so, with no other options,
Tobias returned

23:01.950 --> 23:03.409
to his in-laws' penthouse,

23:03.451 --> 23:06.371
desperate enough
to ransack the place,

23:06.412 --> 23:09.332
when it appeared
someone had beaten him to it.

23:09.374 --> 23:11.168
Michael.

23:11.208 --> 23:12.878
No, George Michael.

